        "body": "Previously, the EventViewSet was disabled due to pretix dependencies, which caused\r\n/api/v1/organizers/<slug>/events/    to return errors.\r\n\r\nThis PR introduces a working EventViewSet using eventyay’s native Event model\r\nand EventSerializer, restoring the organizer events API.\r\n\r\nThis enables clients and frontend components to correctly fetch events\r\nfor a given organizer.\n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nBug Fixes:\n- Restore the /api/v1/organizers/<slug>/events/ endpoint so it returns events instead of errors for a given organizer.",
