        "body": "### Problem\nThe organizer events API endpoint `/api/v1/organizers/{organizer}/events/` is currently disabled and returns errors instead of event data.\n\n### Expected behavior\nThe endpoint should return the list of events for a given organizer.\n\n### Actual behavior\nThe endpoint is disabled due to the EventViewSet being commented out.\n\n### Solution\nRe-enable the endpoint using a ReadOnlyModelViewSet with explicit permissions.\n\nPR: https://github.com/fossasia/eventyay/pull/2160\n",
